[20:02] <camelia> rakudo-moar 20f335: OUTPUT: ¬´Potential difficulties:‚ê§    Precedence of ^ is looser than method call; please parenthesize‚ê§    at <tmp>:1‚ê§    ------> 3^257‚èè5.pick.say‚ê§WARNINGS for <tmp>:‚ê§Useless use of "^" in expression "^25.pick.say" in sink context (line 1)‚ê§25‚ê§¬ª

[20:02] <geekosaur> dmaestro, it's a hack

[20:02] <geekosaur> there's a space before the .

